                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/2494: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Warren</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-04-05T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 5, 1922—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>32. Department’s 31, April 7 [<hi rend="italic">6</hi>], 6 [<hi rend="italic"
                        >7</hi>] p.m.<note n="67" xml:id="d702fn67">Not printed.</note> Advise
                    Stevens of contents of Peking’s No. 118, March 25, 1 p.m., in case you have
                    received it, otherwise Stevens will learn contents upon arrival at Harbin, and
                    also of the desire of the British Government to avoid further expense in
                    connection with the maintenance of the Technical Board. Ask him to discuss
                    situation fully with Wang and others <pb facs="1013" n="893" xml:id="pg_893"/>
                    as he may think best, keeping in close touch with the Minister at Peking as well
                    as yourself and to write the Department at length his considered views
                    respecting future possibilities and American policy.</p>
                <p>Has Foreign Office spoken to you as forecast in Department’s instruction No. 41
                    of February 16?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
